---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const publishedAt = '2026-04-29';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Costco Hot Dog Protein"
  description="A Costco hot dog contains 24g of protein with the bun, or 22g without. Protein breakdown and fitness implications."
  type="article"
  publishedAt={publishedAt}
>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Protein Content</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">How much protein is in a Costco hot dog? More than you might think.</p>

    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl p-8 text-center mb-10">
      <p class="text-sm text-green-700 font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Protein</p>
      <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-green-800 mt-2">24g</p>
      <p class="text-green-700">per hot dog with bun</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">How It Compares</h2>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <table class="w-full">
        <thead class="bg-gray-50"><tr><th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold">Food</th><th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold">Protein</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
          <tr class="bg-green-50"><td class="px-6 py-3 font-medium">Costco Hot Dog</td><td class="px-6 py-3 font-bold">24g</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-6 py-3">McDonald's Big Mac</td><td class="px-6 py-3">25g</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-6 py-3">Large Egg</td><td class="px-6 py-3">6g</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-6 py-3">Chicken Breast (3 oz)</td><td class="px-6 py-3">26g</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="px-6 py-3">Standard Hot Dog</td><td class="px-6 py-3">10g</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">For Fitness</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">At 24g of protein, a Costco hot dog provides nearly half the daily protein needs for an average sedentary adult (RDA: 50g). For active individuals targeting 150g+/day, it's a convenient mid-day protein boost — though the sodium and fat content should be factored into your overall diet.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
